snippet.title: FURTIVE - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
FURTIVE is now available for wishlist on Steam!

WISHLIST NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1514850/FURTIVE/

Website: https://frozenbulletgames.com/furtive
Instagram: https://instagram.com/furtivegame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/furtivegame

Twitter: http://twitter.com/FrozenBulletSTU

FURTIVE:
Prisoners of war, your team was captured but on the run on a large military controlled island. Explore, gather resources, build a shelter and survive the dangerous military presence on the look out for your team in this epic first person, multiplayer, open world, survival adventure.

Music by Fuzzeke: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyP7PwMM151uZMJaFglX8LA/

©2021 Frozen Bullet Studios
